            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "One of the worst school. No proper education and teachers ask student to search answers from the Google. No proper portion completion. Does not deserve even a single star. Those who have given 4-5 star to these school are either paid people by the school management or does not have any visibility of their kids situation. Do not recommend this school to any one.\n\nIf the parents does not want their kids to be in good position or who does not care can join their kids.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
