            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Alard Public School is One of the best school in Hinjewadi. The positive environment and the good vibes is more essential than teaching kids 2+2. Kids grow in carefree atmosphere which reflects in their overall development. I regret I dint know about this school earlier or else would have started from play school.",
